        <mxCell id="rules_body" value="✓  Goals are outcome statements,&#xa;    not task lists&#xa;&#xa;✓  Max 3 primary goals per cycle&#xa;&#xa;✓  Goals must be feasible — if not,&#xa;    split or reduce before committing&#xa;&#xa;✓  Every goal needs an estimate&#xa;    (S · M · L sizing)&#xa;&#xa;✓  Do not start the cycle without&#xa;    Ready items in the backlog&#xa;&#xa;✓  The WIP limit is non-negotiable —&#xa;    post it visibly on the board&#xa;&#xa;✓  This session ends when goals&#xa;    are locked, not when time runs out" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;fontSize=11;fontColor=#94A3B8;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
